00:28:44,756 --> 00:28:45,780
I make some tea.

453
00:28:45,890 --> 00:28:49,553
Are you sure you have room for the two
<i>idiosos</i> that burnt down their house?

454
00:28:49,661 --> 00:28:53,757
<i>Idiotas.</i> And you are not <i>idiotas.</i>
Here, let me help you with those.

455
00:28:53,965 --> 00:28:56,991
I always have room for you two here,
my babies.

456
00:28:57,235 --> 00:29:01,638
- You can stay in my daughters' bedroom.
- You have a daughter?

457
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:05,699
