458
00:29:06,311 --> 00:29:10,907
- Nezy, how come you never told us that?
- Because you never asked. <i>Caliente.</i>

459
00:29:11,516 --> 00:29:13,347
Well, why don't they live here with you?

460
00:29:13,451 --> 00:29:16,784
Have you ever heard
of post-9/11 immigration delays?

461
00:29:18,857 --> 00:29:22,759
The <i>terroristas</i> have won.
