463
00:29:32,437 --> 00:29:34,928
You're gonna feel very comfortable here.

464
00:29:37,976 --> 00:29:39,637
Let me fix this for you.

465
00:29:49,387 --> 00:29:50,354
Good night.

466
00:29:58,863 --> 00:30:01,229
It's so weird not being at home.

467
00:30:02,133 --> 00:30:04,226
It feels weird not having a home.

468
00:30:18,783 --> 00:30:21,775
Ava, why does all this stuff
look so familiar?

469
00:30:23,021 --> 00:30:24,989
'Cause it used to be ours.

470
00:30:25,757 --> 00:30:30,353
