471
00:30:30,461 --> 00:30:33,259
My puppy sticker collection is still here.

472
00:30:34,532 --> 00:30:36,693
My popcorn scratch-and-sniff!

473
00:30:39,137 --> 00:30:41,332
It still smells like popcorn.

474
00:30:45,076 --> 00:30:48,239
